There are 4 potencial types of issues that you could experience with Terraform

Language
State
Core
Provider Errors

1. Example syntax error and you can see in output and error number
2. state is out of sync and Terraform may destroy or change something
of states is locked you will also be blocket for operations
3. These error are directly to main core Terrafrom appllication
Error produced at this level may be a bug
4. These set of error are primarily releated to the provider plugins
Use provider Github page for report an identify issue

